### Register User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

